<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shoulder-vt">shoulder <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ʃəʊldə(r)/    美 /'ʃoʊldər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>承担；担负：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You don’t need to <strong>shoulder the blame</strong> for this failure.
你无须对这次失败承担责任。</p></div></div>